  <mainDescription>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Purpose&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    This metric is used to determine how effective the team is at&amp;nbsp;mitigating project risk. Knowing what action plan to&#xD;
    take before having to execute it can significantly reduce the potential negative impact of a project risk.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Definition&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Count the number of identified risks that do not have a defined mitigation plan. Divide this number by the total number&#xD;
    of identified risks.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Keep in mind that a mitigation plan might be to do nothing to mitigate the risk. This type of plan typically is applied&#xD;
    to low priority/ low impact risks.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Analysis&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    A good way to monitor Percentage of Risks with No Mitigation Plan is to use a simple bar chart.&amp;nbsp; Plot iterations&#xD;
    on the X axis and percentage on the Y axis.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    &lt;strong>Expected Trend&lt;/strong> - All non-trivial risks have a mitigation plan defined.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    If the team is identifying project risks, but not defining mitigation plans, they are not prepared and the project is&#xD;
    not predictable. Each non-trivial risk needs a mitigation plan to ensure that it doesn't materialize and negatively&#xD;
    impact the project. Note that the effort to&amp;nbsp;mitigate risk&amp;nbsp;has an associated cost. The team must balance the&#xD;
    cost of this effort against the potential impact of not addressing the risk. Not all candidate risks are actively&#xD;
    managed. Mitigation effort and degree of monitoring depend on the likelihood of impact and the risk tolerance for the&#xD;
    project.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Frequency and reporting&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Monitor Percentage of Risks with No Mitigation Plan&amp;nbsp;in each iteration during&amp;nbsp;iteration planning.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Collection and reporting tools&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Project Conductor&amp;reg; and IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Team Concert&amp;reg; collect risk data. Create a custom report to monitor&#xD;
    the percentage of risks that do not have mitigation plans.&lt;br />&#xD;
    &amp;nbsp;&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
